         <particDesc>
            <listPerson>
               <person>
                  <persName role="owner" corresp="PRS0000">According to Additio 2, the Ms. was donated by ʾabeto Hagos, most probably a son of däğğazmač Säbagadis Wäldu (s. EAE IV, 431, both died in 1831). The name Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus (e.g., fols. 10va, 32rab, 32vab, 41rab, 50va) is mentioned in the supplication formulas, together with several other names: Gäbrä Ṣadǝq (e.g., fols. 10va, 32rab, 32vab, 41rab, 50va), Zä-Wäldä Maryam (fols. 10va, 32vab, 41ra, 50va), Täsfa Maryam (fols. 32vb, 41rb), Wälättä ʿAbiyä ʾƎgziʾ (fols. 50va, 54ra, 59ra), Wäldä Lǝʿul (fols. 60va, 67vb), Wälättä Ṣǝyon (fols. 59ra, 68va), Wäldä Ḥawaryat and Wäldä Krǝstos (fol. 66vb), Gäbrä Samuʾel (fols. 104vb, 110vb). However, the baptismal name of Hagos is Dagǝmawi Zä-Mänfäs Qǝddus.</persName>
                  <!--ACHTUNG! This is actually paragraphic information identifying the donor. 
                                        Person/persName should only contain the person name, not all the paragraph.-->
               </person>
               <person>
                  <persName corresp="PRS00000"/>
                  <!--other-->
               </person>
            </listPerson>
